# Hello there.
I'm the Conceptionist. I do stuff in JS. Notably, I do bots for Discord. You probably know me for  
## TopHat,
which is probably the best feat in programming I have made so far. That other people can use, anyway.  
  
# Other stuff I do
I work for Mack (@Sven65) as a developer for Discord Dungeons, which is a thing that he's making. I'm less of a developer, and more of a guy that figures out if stuff works. So that's nice.
